{"tid":2138503,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇睇暗瘡西醫介紹？","createTime":"2020-08-03T15:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T18:53:23.000Z","uid":223392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"54a11563a41922f524437d80c154fa7e57321e34","tid":2138503,"uid":223392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:28:22.000Z","msg":"如題，自從帶左口罩塊面係咁狂爆。以家d暗大大粒，唔識爆膿。一直都keep住係到唔上唔落，又唔識謝，keep住紅色。<br />\n或者另外一種，暗瘡謝左之後個印係極之深紅色，個印一直都唔會退。"},{"pid":"0cdd5aa62eb52b2e59c4bc131bb29768fdbbd7cd","tid":2138503,"uid":20025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:57:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"368a6b94c63b5852a18879b00c07b7a5423bb5c2","tid":2138503,"uid":184166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T17:05:13.000Z","msg":"睇西醫都係叫你食a酸"},{"pid":"efcb27eaa1c318a46c554414ab4e379e121795ed","tid":2138503,"uid":209390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T17:53:26.000Z","msg":"我都係T字位係咁爆<br />\n大粒又冇膿<br />\n好不容易謝左一粒附近又會再出一粒新鮮嘅<br />\n深層清潔mask愈fu仲愈衰<br />\n我諗緊睇中醫好唔好"},{"pid":"d1279b1c4898629713bb1c1a2c3dbc07b0de7b37","tid":2138503,"uid":297465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:16:37.000Z","msg":"醫生只會比藥你壓住個病情，但你無解決到個問題"},{"pid":"b7eac19f2154bb0b97fed2d2915ea4e858816e89","tid":2138503,"uid":72701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T16:28:59.000Z","msg":"方慶生醫生，陳方安生細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457aac185aca95c1f630603cb61ac2d085d8f173","tid":2138503,"uid":114584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7eac19f2154bb0b97fed2d2915ea4e858816e89","tid":2138503,"uid":72701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T16:28:59.000Z","msg":"方慶生醫生，陳方安生細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T17:00:53.000Z","msg":"睇緊 正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"